item.title: How to i portforward or w.e?
item.dc:creator: @ultimatepkvillage ultimatepkvillage
item.description:
@ultimatepkvillage wrote:

[quote=“donster111”]Guys idk how to make my server available to others can you help me?

[font=impact]Thanks, Donster[/font][/quote]

[quote=“I am Nick”]in your browser type 192.168.1.1 user admin password admin
press applications and gaming for the application put RSPS for the start and the end put 43594 protocol tcp and for the ip address open up cmd.exe and type ipconfig and it should say a ip address copy the last 3 numbers and put that for the ip address then check enable and press save settings now you are done[/quote]

^^ THATS FOR LINKSYS ROUTERS!

post your router name and model and I’ll try and link a tut to you
